#Shiva: causes Minor damage to enemy.
#
#
if isinbattle caster
	number damage * 120 * 3 rand
	inc enemy caster hp * -1 damage
	inc caster damdone damage
	chat caster concat concat concat concat " You call upon a Guardian Force-Shiva-to attack " name enemy caster " with swift coldness and peircing dimonds shred it's body doing " damage "  damage."
	chat enemy caster concat concat " swift coldness and peircing dimonds shred your body for " damage "  damage."
	endscript
end
chat caster "You must be in battle to use this spell."
endscript








